        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Where would a UI be without the ability to theme it? The Theming system
        makes it incredibly easy to update colors, materials, font settings, etc.
        to keep your application's UI feeling cohesive and coherent. Additionally,
        you can easily add light and dark variants for your theme without any performance
        hitches.\n\n Try it with the button below and see for yourself."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
